Package uk.co.dancowan.robots.srv.hal.commands.camera

Class Summary
GrabBinCmd Grab the contents of the configured colour bin.
GrabBlobCmd Request blob information for the configured colour bin.
GrabImageCmd Grabs and decodes an java.awt.Image from the SRV camera.
GrabPixelsCmd Grab the colour information for the configured area.
PixelGrabber Class to grab a pixel from the camera and set it to a colour bin via the configured receiver class.
SetBinCmd Extension of AbstractCommand which sets the parameters of a colour bin on the SRV1q.
SetResolutionCmd Command sets the resolution of the camera image.
